<style>
  .auth-shell {
    max-width: 440px;
    margin: 60px auto 0;
    animation: scaleIn var(--duration-slow) var(--ease-out) both;
  }

  .auth-card {
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-2xl);
    padding: 36px;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .auth-card::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    height: 3px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--brand), var(--brand-hover), var(--accent-blue));
    border-radius: 3px 3px 0 0;
  }

  .auth-card h1 {
    font-size: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    margin-top: 8px;
  }

  .auth-card p {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .field-group {
    margin-bottom: 18px;
  }

  .submit-btn {
    margin-top: 12px;
    width: 100%;
    padding: 14px 18px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .foot-note {
    margin-top: 20px;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 14px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .foot-note a {
    color: var(--brand);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .foot-note a:hover {
    color: var(--brand-hover);
  }
</style>

<div class="auth-shell">
  <div class="auth-card">
    <h1>欢迎回来</h1>
    <p>继续你上次没聊完的话。你可以用用户名、邮箱或者手机号登录。</p>
    <form method="POST" action="/login">
      <div class="field-group">
        <label for="login">账号</label>
        <input id="login" name="login" maxlength="120" required placeholder="用户名 / 邮箱 / 手机号" />
      </div>
      <div class="field-group">
        <label for="password">密码</label>
        <input id="password" name="password" type="password" maxlength="100" required placeholder="输入密码" />
      </div>
      <button class="submit-btn" type="submit">登录</button>
    </form>
    <div class="foot-note">第一次来？<a href="/register">注册账号 →</a></div>
  </div>
</div>